    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Under the Minimal profile, the UnitOfAssurance is accepted for archival and traceability purposes. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated; 7 are formally assessed with achieved levels uniformly below required levels, and 6 represent epistemic gaps at MRL 5. The package documents the full scope of credibility deficiencies for the VAD hemolysis prediction use case. An inline Requirement object (https://uofa.net/morrison/req/cou2-hemolysis-threshold) is present in the package and describes the absolute hemolysis threshold requirement; however, the formal bindsRequirement assertion at the UnitOfAssurance level has not been established, representing a structural incompleteness consistent with W-SI-02. This package is accepted at Minimal profile for record-keeping; regulatory submission would require upgrade to Complete profile with all binding assertions resolved.",
